        "subject": "DDN-185 ofd: LDLM lock should cover object destroy",
        "message": "DDN-185 ofd: LDLM lock should cover object destroy\n\nThe exclusive PW lock protecting OST object destroy should be\nreleased after object destroy procedure.\n\nQuench error messages of object unavailability when trying to cancel\na LDLM lock, LDLM lock and OST object are not strongly tied.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam.xu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I65c0f966438603df2d493f1c9fa1004bcc4c566d\n"
      },
